    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《塔罗潜能之境》这款轻度类Rogue牌组构筑游戏，以塔罗牌为主题，非常注重连锁反应，将战术摆位和华丽动态的连招巧妙融合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将化身愚人，运用纯粹潜能的力量，改写塔罗牌的规则，进入潜能空间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/67ead974eb9b61bbad6f95461473ba11.poster.avif?t=1768240177\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/67ead974eb9b61bbad6f95461473ba11.webm?t=1768240177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/67ead974eb9b61bbad6f95461473ba11.mp4?t=1768240177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>策略与混沌</strong><br>摆出牌阵进行解读。每个花色各有各的能力，即便花色花色相同，不同的牌展现的效果也各不相同。搭配卡牌，合理摆放，打出各种连招。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/b01e0d88fc8ba5cce66e933b944a43d2.poster.avif?t=1768240177\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/b01e0d88fc8ba5cce66e933b944a43d2.webm?t=1768240177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/b01e0d88fc8ba5cce66e933b944a43d2.mp4?t=1768240177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>越来越强</strong><br>从零开始，逐渐获得塔罗牌。游戏中的塔罗牌与现实世界的版本不同，每种大阿尔卡那都拓展成为一个含有14张牌的花色。改变你的塔罗牌，赋予它们额外的属性，同时获得决定构筑玩法的升级选项。每一次遭遇战都有可能成就或中断你的旅程。350多张牌、150多个升级选项等你解锁，更有数十个地点等你探索，各有各的特殊机制。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/287ab5f068bcd7ea3622d3ecf1dd593a.poster.avif?t=1768240177\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/287ab5f068bcd7ea3622d3ecf1dd593a.webm?t=1768240177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/287ab5f068bcd7ea3622d3ecf1dd593a.mp4?t=1768240177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>通过阿尔卡那试炼</strong><br>接受阿尔卡那试炼，通过其中的艰苦考验。21张大阿尔卡那，每张都有一项阿尔卡那试炼，各有各的难题等你逐一破解。展现你的实力，全部破解，揭示你的前路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/fed79dfc93a0fa4749a5202d0fdd4738.poster.avif?t=1768240177\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/fed79dfc93a0fa4749a5202d0fdd4738.webm?t=1768240177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219850/extras/fed79dfc93a0fa4749a5202d0fdd4738.mp4?t=1768240177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>叙事借鉴了塔罗牌的主题</strong><br>化身愚人，踏上理解自我的旅程，了解自己神圣力量的极限。明白以太世界和凡人世界究竟为何扭曲。其他大阿尔卡那在等你。</p>",
